{"tid":1180850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個好撚小氣嘅朋友做過嘅事","createTime":"2019-06-01T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T10:00:10.000Z","uid":228002,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfe5514868016c731b24c41f35c8afa4029e028","tid":1180850,"uid":228002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"話說早排玩交友apps嘅時候用班friend嘅相同佢地電話黎做自我介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家都知道我攞嚟玩一兩日就會del，所以唔係好care，但唯獨是有個friend A反應好大，唔想我咁玩，仲搶咗我部手機要求我del咗佢，咁事後我都del咗啲資料亦都del埋個交友apps，但A就係因為咁樣嬲咗我幾日亦都冇同我有任何交流過， 直到尋日朝早我收到個咁嘅電話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀sir：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 喂，係咪xxx？<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 我係，請問咩事？<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 你係咪有個同學仔姓X？(A個姓)<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 係呀我係佢同學 ，請問你係邊個？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 喂，呢度警務處打嚟，你係咪用佢啲個人資料你玩交友apps？ 而家佢上咗嚟警局同我地詐曬型， 如果你再咁玩落去我就落案&hellip;&hellip;（ 餘下幾十句都係不停咁恐嚇我）<br />\n<br />\n   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 我係有玩呀，但係嗰個apps我已經del咗喇喎。(當時我嚇撚到瀨屎但同時亦都滿頭問號Jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我唔理你啦， 你個同學有圖畀我哋睇你係用佢啲個人資料你玩交友apps，如果你畀我哋查撚到你冇del佢啲個人資料，咁你自己麻煩㗎咋後生仔。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;（ 我當時喺度諗緊係咪佢搶咗我部電話嗰陣時影低咗相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就話畀十分鐘時間我開返個apps cap圖畀A睇，證明我已經del晒啲資料乜乜77如果唔係就落案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住就cut咗線&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我本身都係半信半疑，我以為佢搵佢啲friend或者老豆打過嚟恐嚇我咁啦，但當我上網check返個電話嗰陣時候，原來真係警務處打嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嘩屌我嗰下真係呆撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我坐咗喺部電腦前面呆咗十分鐘先識得反應， 點解呢個世界可以有人小氣到咁嘅地步，你已經刷新咗我對小氣呢個詞語嘅認知， 恐怕喺日後我再遇到小氣嘅人都只會認為佢哋只係芝麻綠豆嘅事， 因為全世界都冇可能與你匹敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqanoKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqanoKO.jpg&h=c97a91d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOtcLYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOtcLYw.jpg&h=64a08e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6494f89baacb3dafc8efbac911daa5efcc44a25","tid":1180850,"uid":251665,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"好明顯你唔啱wor<br />\n幾歲？中學雞？玩埋啲咁幼稚嘅嘢<br />\n其實你知唔知醜？"},{"pid":"d083ac01fd42589aa322ec6d1e8cabdf0cee5a13","tid":1180850,"uid":51294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"自己唔啱話人小氣？"},{"pid":"154ed451eee2af6932c4f2027ca84ed68ae20dba","tid":1180850,"uid":10903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"咁樣擺明係你唔撚啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學畢業未？"},{"pid":"fb3a2dd458a18adb7f92f07537fd8ee9810f6754","tid":1180850,"uid":21788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔俾你玩就係人地小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a0ff2405571b32ff01c54f20d99b996b882fd5","tid":1180850,"uid":250041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"試下人地咁玩你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1183ac8f5cd1856948c19685d90b06a60ac2681","ti